      <title>纽约学校因家长反对而撤销手机禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nyc-schools-reverse-course-on-cell-phone-ban-after-parents-balk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市教育局长戴维·班克斯 (David Banks) 表示“现在还不是”在学校禁止使用手机的时候，他提到了上个月上西区两所学校封锁期间家长难以联系到孩子这一担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nyc-schools-reverse-course-on-cell-phone-ban-after-parents-balk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Visa 推出平台帮助银行在全球范围内发行稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/visa-launches-platform-to-help-banks-issue-stablecoins-globally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的金融机构和企业对加密货币和区块链技术如何改善其运营表现出兴趣，Visa Inc. 正在推出一个供银行发行法定支持的代币（如稳定币和代币化存款）的平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/visa-launches-platform-to-help-banks-issue-stablecoins-globally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电推出单一股票 ETF，Direxion 基金允许杠杆投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/tsmc-gets-single-stock-etf-as-direxion-funds-allow-leverage-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Direxion Funds 推出了两只专注于一只新兴市场股票 — — 台湾半导体制造股份有限公司 — — 的交易所交易产品，允许投资者对其做超额看涨押注，或采取与市场走势相反的仓位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/tsmc-gets-single-stock-etf-as-direxion-funds-allow-leverage-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PayPal 使用稳定币完成首笔商业交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/paypal-completes-its-first-business-transaction-using-stablecoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PayPal Holdings Inc. 使用其专有的稳定币完成了首笔商业支付，以展示如何使用数字货币来改善通常笨拙的商业交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/paypal-completes-its-first-business-transaction-using-stablecoin</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
