      <title>旅客需要了解的有关欧盟新边境检查的信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/eu-s-new-entry-exit-system-what-ees-biometric-data-rules-mean-for-travellers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在加紧推行新的边境控制系统计划，以处理每年访问欧盟的数亿人，尽管有人怀疑该系统是否能在下个月的启动日期之前完成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/eu-s-new-entry-exit-system-what-ees-biometric-data-rules-mean-for-travellers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:21:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行将于 2025 年开始使用 Swift 进行代币交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/banks-set-to-use-swift-for-token-transactions-starting-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从明年开始，商业银行和中央银行将能够在 Swift 消息网络上进行数字资产交易的实时试验，推动区块链技术的广泛机构采用更接近现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/banks-set-to-use-swift-for-token-transactions-starting-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SAP、Carahsoft 调查范围扩大至近 100 家机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的法庭记录，美国检察官正在扩大对德国软件制造商 SAP SE 和技术经销商 Carahsoft Technology Corp. 可能存在的价格操纵的调查，试图调查这两家公司与近 100 个政府机构的合作情况，调查范围远远超出之前所知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
